<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="slightly-adv">slightly <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'slaɪtli/    美 /'slaɪtli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>略微；稍微</strong></h4>
<p>a little</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His body shook slightly because he was afraid.
因为害怕，他的身体微微颤抖着。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 2</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Canada’s population is only slightly over thirty million.
加拿大的人口只有3000万多一点。</p><footer>人教③ – 5</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>It is <strong><em>_</em></strong> (slight) colder today than it was yesterday.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. slightly  </p></div>